{"tid":1281314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到記者爭人錢唔還比人打","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T09:22:41.000Z","uid":15440,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"78917fd3523f766e38e4942f58c0efb9e6d5599f","tid":1281314,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UdXM1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UdXM1c.png&h=7213e8df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說睇完份野之後發夢見到記者爭人錢唔還比人打<br />\n<br />\n發夢係條天橋見到有兩個黑衣人圍住個男人鬧幾時還錢，拖左工程費好耐，對罵左幾分鐘。<br />\n個位疑似記者就話你自己問呀爺攞囉，係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欠債還錢天經地義，原來有呀爺懷抱可以唔洗還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n欠債比人打仲會有人發聲明 入落暴徒誤導讀者以為同某行動有關，你地如果爭落周身街數唔洗申請破產架啦，搵呀爺就搞點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保證無人郁你"},{"pid":"b2fbf179dabb9f5570fcd9c192b945356c04c9a3","tid":1281314,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人發夢係入面做知內情係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係路過聽到幾句炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87990000c43bcc049abe998ba8dd4465aa9dbc12","tid":1281314,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c93aa5b54293a86d165b3c4ffa77cc0cdc27b53","tid":1281314,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"唔洗發夢，係有消息人士透露"},{"pid":"3a1c4ac6234b44c267fe6036935bc097345049e9","tid":1281314,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c93aa5b54293a86d165b3c4ffa77cc0cdc27b53",